Converts a [`String`] reference into a [`Borrowed`] variant.
No heap allocation is performed, and the string
is not copied.

# Example

```
# use std::borrow::Cow;
let s = "eggplant".to_string();
assert_eq!(Cow::from(&s), Cow::Borrowed("eggplant"));
```

